{
  "texts": [
    "This work ensures that a two-stage VAE produces high-quality images without the blurred edges specific for VAEs, although GANs are still superior in this context to the two-stage VAE.",
    "A hierarchical VAE, proposed under the name of Nouveau VAE (Vahdat and Kautz 2020), is similar to a two-stage VAE.",
    "This method ensures that the architecture has multiple latent spaces on different levels.",
    "All of them have the usual elements, like reparameterization trick.",
    "The residual blocks are situated between the latent layers, and they act like very simple encoder or decoder between the layers."
  ]
}